                \b both must be irretrievably lost for ever". 
                \b Believing the great general Marlborough would join him, on 23 August James wrote to the Duke of Berwick, 
                \b his illegitimate brother and Marlborough's nephew, that; "I think it is now more than ever Now or Never".
        
